iana.encoding_considerations:
Security considerations: dspx+json shares security issues that are common to application/json as defined in RFC4627 Section #6 (https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc4627.html). This media type is not expected to contain any active or executable content. Information contained in dspx+json documents does not require privacy or integrity services.

Interoperability considerations: None.

Published specification: https://github.com/diffscope/opendspx/blob/main/docs/dspx-spec.md

Applications which use this media: DiffScope compatible editors.
